tmail

Start your long job and forget it. When the job finishes,
tmail will email you.


USAGE

1. Copy .tmail.conf into your $HOME and edit it. You know how.
2. chmod +x tmail
3. Copy tmail into somewhere in your $PATH.
4. tmail COMMAND
5. Count down 10s.
6. If the job does not finish in 10s, then you can forget it
   and do other things. You will receive an email once the
   job finishes.

